Novak Djokovic beat Tomas Berdych 7-5 4-6 6-3 in the final of the Monte Carlo Open on Sunday . 
  The world No 1 is the first player to win the opening three Masters 1000 events of the season . 
  He beat Rafael Nadal in the first round of the clay court season . 
  The Serbian defeated the Czech in three sets . 
 